      "updated": 1776171170647,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Fast explanation:\n1) main is an integration branch, so it can be ahead of PROD.\n2) Normal release: create a release branch with only the approved changes.\n3) PROD bug: create a hotfix branch from the exact PROD baseline, not from the latest main.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Fast explanation:\n1) main is an integration branch, so it can be ahead of PROD.\n2) Normal release: create a release branch with only the approved changes.\n3) PROD bug: create a hotfix branch from the exact PROD baseline, not from the latest main.",
